Fossa is a graphical control application for analysis, manipulation, and 
synthesis of digitized sounds using Loris sound library (http://www.cerlsoundgroup.org/Loris/).

The primary distribution point for Fossa is SourceForge
(http://loris.sourceforge.net).

Fossa is free software. Please see the file COPYING for details.

For a list of major changes to Loris, organized by release number,
please see the file NEWS.

For installation instructions, please see the file INSTALL.

